title: Freshly Inked - July 2013
description:
Freshly Inked - July 2013

100 Pages | HQ PDF | English | 12 MB 


Freshly Inked is a platform for emerging and established tattoo artists from around the world to showcase their artwork. It serves as a look book designed to help satiate an audience of tattoo enthusiasts looking for vibrant pages of tattoo designs, styles and trends.  Every issue Freshly Inked identifies 12-14 of the most talented artists, featuring a portfolio of their best work. Featured artists also share their professional history and goals with readers.
